  "system": {
    "description": "<p>During the [Damage Apply Step], you receive the expected HP damage that a target other than yourself would have received. The target receives no damage. You do not receive any Bad Statuses as a result of this substitution. You can only use this skill once in response to any given attack.<br><br>The moment an ally receives a wound, your devotion is a magic that transfers it to yourself instead. A devotional prayer can save a friend from danger.</p>",
